cs.DC, cs.DS, cs.NA, cs.AI, cs.SY

Reasoning: 
- cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) is the most likely category as the paper deals with process mapping in parallel applications on distributed memory systems. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is also likely as the paper presents algorithms for solving the quadratic assignment problem. 
- cs.NA (Numerical Analysis) is another possibility as the paper deals with optimization algorithms. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper uses local search algorithms to improve the mappings. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is a less likely category, but still possible as the paper deals with communication systems and their hierarchy.
